text: Chuvash-Kubovo () is a rural locality (a selo) and the administrative center of Chuvash-Kubovsky Selsoviet, Iglinsky District, Bashkortostan, Russia. The population was 1,602 as of 2010. There are 29 streets. == Geography == It is located on the left bank of the Lobovka River, 10 km from Iglino. == References == Category:Rural localities in Iglinsky District
title: Chuvash-Kubovo
